{"lastModified":1773178666652,"uri":"c::8356249384::vessel::d5cc4e73-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: West Mediterranean, East Mediterranean, Croatia, Montenegro, France, Italy, Greece, Monaco, Sardinia, Corsica\n\nExquisitely finished, superbly equipped, Trident was designed to provide charter guests with unprecedented levels of hospitality and service. \n\nTrident can accommodate up to twelve guests in eight staterooms, with one full-beam master stateroom with king size bed, his and her bathrooms and dressing room on main deck, one VIP stateroom and five convertible guest staterooms. The crew of 15 are equipped with everything to make an owner’s or guests stay on board perfect, with state-of-the-art galley, bars and comfortable accommodation. The modern and elegant interior was designed by Donald Starkey. The top deck jacuzzi and deck areas feature massive spaces for seating, dining and lounging. She has also a gym on the sundeck and an elevator. Trident carries an incredible selection of water toys and beach toys. She has a cruising speed 14 knots and is equipped with an ultra-modern stabilisation system complete with an at-anchor stabiliser.","blueprint":{"name":"TRIDENT","images":["/media/media::image::c::8356249384::vessel::d5cc4e73-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::iMaITA9YI.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8356249384::vessel::d5cc4e73-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-101206-zi673mMOt.PNG/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8356249384::vessel::d5cc4e73-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-101206-j44PLJgDz.PNG/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8356249384::vessel::d5cc4e73-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-101206-ih1h_M9k-.PNG/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8356249384::vessel::d5cc4e73-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-101206-G90VWSJSG.PNG/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8356249384::vessel::d5cc4e73-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::as